data.description: Experience luxury living and marvel at the awe-inspiring panoramic views of the cityscape right from the heart of Atlantic Station! Nestled in the flagship condo complex of Atlantic Station, this stunning 2 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom end unit condo is a perfect blend of elegance and modern living PLUS all the amenities you've been looking for.    The stylish interiors will captivate you and the natural light through floor-to-ceiling windows in the living area highlights an unparalleled panoramic view, creating a picturesque backdrop for your everyday life. The posh and expansive modern eat-in kitchen is a chef's dream, boasting a bar counter with stone countertops, beautifully stained cabinets, stainless steel appliances, and a built-in wine rack that adds a touch of sophistication to the space. You can also unwind on the balcony — a perfect retreat with its stunning views that capture the golden hour in all its glory. The layout is designed for privacy and comfort, ideal for a roommate plan. The main bedroom features a walk-in closet and an ensuite bathroom with a double vanity, a separate soaking tub, and a glass-enclosed shower.    Noteworthy updates include a recently replaced furnace in July 2023, ensuring efficient and modern heating for your comfort. The building itself is a haven of amenities designed to elevate your lifestyle, including a pool, on-site gym, lounge area, and 24-hour concierge services. As a unit owner, enjoy the convenience of extra storage upon request from the building manager and benefit from two assigned parking spaces. The community is gated, offering security and peace of mind, this residence is strategically located with proximity to popular stores like Ikea, Publix, Target, and other Atlantic Station landmarks. Don't miss the opportunity to call this prime residence your home and indulge in the epitome of luxury living in Atlanta.
